                        <lb n="5" break="no"/>mānaM vimānaM vīraścakre mala
                        <lb n="6" break="no"/>yajamahīmaṇḍana<unclear>ṃ</unclear> sundareśaḥ <g ref="sym:tam-pillaiyarCuli" type="punctuation"/></l>
